    "description": "Juicy Chemistry Asia Pacific Associates invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of SEO Specialist at our Hyderabad location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Juicy Chemistry Asia Pacific Associates:\nJuicy Chemistry Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Magento\n• Proficiency in Affiliate Marketing\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Learning & development budget\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Hyderabad, Telangana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Juicy Chemistry Asia Pacific Associates!",
